{"tid":1888630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖解釋如何防止武肺入屋","createTime":"2020-02-20T10:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T11:28:56.000Z","uid":39021,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"09cb58637e9645324759da91c101e8f0a4932dac","tid":1888630,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8az13ev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8az13ev.jpg&h=c6c2750f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n絕大部份中招既其實都係<strong>老人家</strong><br />\n<br />\n老人家中招，唔止係因為佢地抵抗力弱，仲因為佢地普遍<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懶醒</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n廢老四宗罪：<br />\n第一，明明可以隔幾日先買餸，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持日日落街買新鮮餸</span></strong>，你鬧佢時候，佢會反駁話個個都係咁落街架啦，但實情係大部份落街既都係班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，繼續<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">落街飲茶</span></strong>，除晒口罩食野，唔荒唔中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重用口罩</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為自己既醒目秘招可以消毒口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外大部份老人家改唔到摸臉習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四，鍾意<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">落街排隊買罩搶紙巾</span></strong>，其實排隊係極之危險既行為，一大班人近距離企埋一齊，隨時一個傳十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你平時做足防疫措施，只要你家庭有一件唔聽話既廢老<br />\n等同中門大開，除褲等比武肺中出<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要防範武肺入屋，一定要完全禁止廢老出門</span></strong>"},{"pid":"35f5e6a3efe33ce2bb9f72d373955b3ab10f9598","tid":1888630,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7a